DeepSpec (DSpark) — https://github.com/deepseek-ai/DeepSpec
License: MIT
Copyright (c) 2026 The DeepSpec Authors
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The DSpark algorithm (semi-autoregressive block drafter, Markov head,
calibrated confidence head, and confidence-scheduled verification) originates
from DeepSeek's DeepSpec project and paper. DeepSpec's PyTorch implementation
is the correctness reference for this port, and portions of the modeling and
verification semantics are adapted from it.

